onDiagnosticsError.prompt:
Type error in {{file}}:

{{diagnostics}}

Do NOT fix the error yet. First: call getCallHierarchy (incoming) to understand what depends on this symbol. Then explain what the type error means and what the safest fix would be. Keep response ≤12 lines.

onGitCommit.prompt:
Commit on {{branch}}: {{message}}
Files: {{files}}

Post-commit health check:
1. getDiagnostics — errors only
2. If any non-test files changed in {{files}}, call runTests and report pass/fail
3. Flag any changed files that lack test coverage
